ns/emoji/unicode/1f4dd.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" alt=\"Lecture Notes\" title=\"Lecture Notes\">\n<ul>\n<li>The purpose of this course is to introduce you to basics of modeling, design, planning, and control of robot systems. In essence, the material treated in this course is a brief survey of relevant results from geometry, kinematics, statics, dynamics, and control.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-29T03:29:44.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"vuejs/awesome-vue","categoryHTML":"<h2>Projects Using Vue.js</h2><h3>Open Source</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/NNTin/discord-logo\">discord-logo</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/NNTin/discord-logo\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">57</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":57,\"repo\":\"NNTin/discord-logo\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A Vue.js animated discord logo generator based on SVGs. (<a href=\"https://nntin.github.io/discord-logo/\">Github Page</a>)</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-29T01:41:04.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"donnemartin/awesome-aws","categoryHTML":"<h2>Open Source Repos</h2><h3>DynamoDB</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/awslabs/dynamodb-geo\">dynamodb-geo 🔥🔥</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/awslabs/dynamodb-geo\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\">